sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Server as Guardrails Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Colang as Colang Runtime
    participant InputRails as Input Rails<br/>(Jailbreak, Injection,<br/>Topic Safety, PII)
    participant LLM as LLM Inference Endpoint<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OutputRails as Output Rails<br/>(Hallucination, Content Safety,<br/>Fact Check, Self Check)
    participant Redis as Redis (optional)<br/>6379/TCP

    Note over Client,Redis: Flow 1: Chat Completion with Guardrails

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP (plaintext, platform-level auth)
    Server->>Server: Load thread context

    opt Thread persistence enabled
        Server->>Redis: Retrieve conversation thread<br/>Redis protocol (optional TLS)
        Redis-->>Server: Thread history
    end

    Server->>Colang: Process input through Colang flows
    Colang->>InputRails: Evaluate input rails
    InputRails->>InputRails: Jailbreak detection (YARA rules)
    InputRails->>InputRails: Injection detection
    InputRails->>InputRails: Topic safety check
    InputRails->>InputRails: PII detection (Presidio)
    InputRails-->>Colang: Input rail results

    alt Input blocked by rails
        Colang-->>Server: Blocked response
        Server-->>Client: Guardrail violation response
    else Input passes rails
        Server->>LLM: Forward to LLM<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: API Key / Bearer Token
        LLM-->>Server: LLM Response

        Colang->>OutputRails: Evaluate output rails
        OutputRails->>OutputRails: Hallucination detection
        OutputRails->>OutputRails: Content safety check
        OutputRails->>OutputRails: Fact checking
        OutputRails->>OutputRails: Self-consistency check
        OutputRails-->>Colang: Output rail results

        alt Output blocked by rails
            Colang-->>Server: Blocked/modified response
            Server-->>Client: Guardrail-filtered response
        else Output passes rails
            Server-->>Client: JSON Response
        end
    end

    opt Thread persistence enabled
        Server->>Redis: Store updated thread
    end

    Note over Client,Redis: Flow 2: Streaming Response (SSE)

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>stream: true
    Server->>LLM: Streaming inference request<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+
    loop SSE Stream
        LLM-->>Server: Token chunk
        Server-->>Client: SSE event (HTTP chunked)
    end
    Server-->>Client: SSE [DONE]
